of the class you want to create.

00:27:40.726 --> 00:27:42.236 A:middle
Here I'm going to
create a vehicle.

00:27:42.886 --> 00:27:44.606 A:middle
And all of the class's
definition,

00:27:44.606 --> 00:27:45.606 A:middle
